text: Catapausa bimaculipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1956. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Catapausa bimaculipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1956
